; NSIS installer stub for Atulya Desktop (Windows)
; Tauri generates the actual installer; this file provides
; customisation hooks if needed in the future.
;
; See: https://v2.tauri.app/distribute/windows-installer/
;
; Custom actions can be added here for:
; - Registry entries
; - Firewall rules (loopback exemption for UWP if needed)
; - Start menu shortcuts
; - Uninstall cleanup of runtime data directory
